2.3 The Triad Balance Algorithm

The core innovation: Dynamic priority weighting based on system state.

```
function calculateModulePriority(systemState) {
  // Each module votes on priority based on its perspective
  const michaelPriority = assessThreatLevel(systemState.threats) * 0.4;
  const gabrielPriority = assessConfusionLevel(systemState.userInteractions) * 0.3;
  const raphaelPriority = assessDegradationLevel(systemState.performance) * 0.3;
  
  // Apply temporal context (recent focus dampening)
  const temporalWeights = applyRecencyBias(lastFocusedModules);
  
  // Calculate final balanced priorities
  return normalizePriorities([
    michaelPriority * temporalWeights.michael,
    gabrielPriority * temporalWeights.gabriel, 
    raphaelPriority * temporalWeights.raphael
  ]);
}
```

