Level Name Michael Capability Gabriel Capability Raphael Capability Integration Level
0 Siloed Basic rule-based security Simple chatbots Threshold-based alerts None
1 Coordinated ML anomaly detection Context-aware responses Automated remediation Manual orchestration
2 Integrated Predictive threat hunting Proactive communication Prescriptive optimization API-based coordination
3 Symbiotic Adversarial simulation Empathetic interaction Autonomous healing Neural shared context
4 Transcendent Ecosystem defense Cross-system translation Evolutionary optimization Consciousness-like emergence

4.2 Evolutionary Pathways

· Path A (Security-First): Michael leads → integrates Gabriel for alerts → integrates Raphael for recovery
· Path B (UX-First): Gabriel leads → integrates Michael for trust → integrates Raphael for performance
· Path C (Ops-First): Raphael leads → integrates Michael for resilience → integrates Gabriel for transparency

